# 🧠 Concept 1: System Thinking (The Master Skill)

## Why Some Students Forget Everything

Many students learn:

```text
Process
Thread
Cache
Paging
Scheduling
```

as separate topics.

Then they forget.

---

## How Engineers Think

Engineers think:

```text
Entire System
```

instead of isolated concepts.

---

## Example: Opening Instagram

What actually happens?

### Step 1

App sends request.

(Networking)

---

### Step 2

OS schedules process.

(OS Scheduling)

---

### Step 3

CPU executes instructions.

(COA)

---

### Step 4

Data loaded from memory.

(Cache + RAM)

---

### Step 5

Database queried.

(Indexing)

---

### Step 6

Data retrieved from distributed servers.

(Distributed Systems)

---

### Step 7

Response returned.

(API Systems)

---

### Step 8

AI recommendation generated.

(AI Infrastructure)

